Package game.actions.actorActions

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ActivateAction
    Represents an action in the game, allowing an actor to activate the SiteOfLostGrace that enables them to fast travel to it or respawn from it.
    ConsumeAction
    Action to consume.
    DeathAction
    An action executed if an actor is killed.
    RemoveActorAction
    Action to remove actor from map and unregister from Managers.
    ResetAction
    ResetAction class.
    RestAction
    Represents a rest action in the game, allowing an actor to rest at a specific location.
    SummonAction
    Represents a summon action in the game, allowing an actor to summon an ally or invader using the SummonSign.
    TravelAction
    Represents a travel action in the game, allowing an actor to travel from one location to another using GoldenFogDoor or SiteofLostGrace.
